headline: Targa Resources Corp. Launches Non-Binding Open Season for Natural Gas Pipeline in the Delaware Basin
summary: HOUSTON, Sept. 02, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Targa Resources Corp. (NYSE: TRGP) (“Targa” or the “Company”) announced today the launch of a non-binding open season for its proposed Forza Pipeline Project (“Forza Project”), a new interstate natural gas pipeline that will support increasing natural gas production in the Delaware Basin in Southeast New Mexico.
